{"tid":2509240,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜濤周五生日　電車公司安排「姜濤號」往返石塘咀至北角賀壽","createTime":"2021-04-29T09:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T10:25:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":98,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"206a88e862c8781b14ce0f4a15b7c6da811fa23e","tid":2509240,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"人氣男子跳唱組合Mirror成員姜濤明日（4月30日）生日，近日有歌迷於多處投放廣告為偶像慶祝，甚至包起電車刊登車身廣告。<br />\n<br />\n電車公司今日於社交媒體表示，會安排有姜濤廣告的電車「姜濤號」，主要行駛來往石塘咀至北角的路線，並會行經登出多幅姜濤廣告，又稱為「姜濤灣」的百德新街站（53E）。<br />\n<br />\n姜濤明日22歲生日，由於姜濤居於銅鑼灣，一眾粉絲「姜糖」近日於銅鑼灣、中灣一帶落重廣告，慶祝偶像姜濤生日，當中編號5號的電車，全車已印上姜濤賀壽的廣告，搖身一變成為「姜濤號」電車。<br />\n<br />\n電車公司今日於Facebook專頁表示，位於百德新街，屬於電車東行線的53E站，又稱為「姜濤灣」，因為姜濤居於銅鑼灣，而且姜濤廣告經常出現於銅鑼灣，結果連續3年都有歌迷「包起」該車站的廣告。<br />\n<br />\n電車公司續指，會盡力安排「姜濤號」行駛來往石塘咀及北角的路線，令「姜濤號」不斷穿梭於「姜濤灣」，以滿足「姜糖」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210429/464487114256420864796231.jpeg/fji40bkWywCa_EdEIA2gUzrQ511AHAItuFH35K1R9-Q?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210429%2F464487114256420864796231.jpeg%2Ffji40bkWywCa_EdEIA2gUzrQ511AHAItuFH35K1R9-Q%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8a9abc47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210429/464487124331663360782106.jpeg/Uhfn9iQiHyI0lDheLR8d88xSgdYqof_go_z267r89us?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210429%2F464487124331663360782106.jpeg%2FUhfn9iQiHyI0lDheLR8d88xSgdYqof_go_z267r89us%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1edaa646&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210429/464487126621884416043678.jpeg/K6FcQdquUXYfFdfv8-yFwZ_joGHaTuXzgrlHipe5R4o?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210429%2F464487126621884416043678.jpeg%2FK6FcQdquUXYfFdfv8-yFwZ_joGHaTuXzgrlHipe5R4o%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=920d0c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/ima